# ActiveDirectoryLAB
STEP 1: Create Lab environments

A) Started with downloading Windows 2022 and Windows 11 ISO from [](https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/evalcenter)
  
  Created Windows server 2022 VM with boot ISO: 
    -Emulate Windows machine
    -Default Machine:Intel ICH9 based PC (2009,x86_64) 
    -6144 MB RAM
    -Default CPU cores
    -Storage: 64 GB
    -Network: Shared Network

  Created Windows 11 Enterprise VM with boot ISO:
    -Virtualize Windows machine
    -4096 MB RAM
    -4 CPU cores
    -Storage: 64 GB
    -Network: Shared Network
